<c74object name='sp.karplus~' category='' module='SP-Tools'>
    <digest>Extended Karplus-Strong resonant string model</digest>
    <description>Extended Karplus-Strong resonant string model.</description>
    <discussion>    <h4><openfilelink filename="SP-Tools Overview.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
    <p>The <o>sp.karplus~</o> object creates a flurry of triggers (or gates) after each input based on the current parameter settings. Can be used to trigger more processes down the line.</p>
</discussion>

